body.raw:
## Introduction

Hello everyone, welcome to my brand new blog. this blog will serve as a place where i can post updates on
my projects, personal life, development ideas and more. Overtime im hoping it will grow into a place where i
can inspire and help other developers with their future endeavors!

i am also working on new things and experimenting with ways to make my current projects and ideas even better
then before, i have years of development experience and enjoy putting it all to good use.

---

## Plans for this website

Overtime i will expand this portfolio and blog and add as much as i can to allow you to get to know me better,
interact with my projects and see the world through my eyes. As of right now the website is good enough for
production use but i am planning on adding more features such as code snippets, wider project showcase and
more in the very near future

---
